spec.description: Comprehensive dashboard for Grafana Faro - web vitals, errors, performance, logs, and user sessions

spec.expr: sum(count_over_time({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"}  | logfmt | kind="measurement" | page_url!="" [$__auto]))
quantile_over_time(0.50, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=web-vital" | json | name="FCP" | unwrap value [$__auto]) by (meta_page_url)
quantile_over_time(0.75, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=web-vital" | json | name="FCP" | unwrap value [$__auto]) by (meta_page_url)
quantile_over_time(0.95, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=web-vital" | json | name="FCP" | unwrap value [$__auto]) by (meta_page_url)
sum by(exception_type) (rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=exception" | json [$__auto]))
sum by(meta_page_url) (rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=exception" | json [$__auto]))
{service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=exception" | json
sum by(meta_page_url) (rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=measurement" | json | meta_page_url!="" [$__auto]))
sum by(session_attributes_user_agent_browser) (rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=measurement" | json | session_attributes_user_agent_browser!="" [$__auto]))
quantile_over_time(0.50, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=measurement" | json | unwrap duration(value_page_load_time) [$__auto]) by (meta_page_url)
quantile_over_time(0.95, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=measurement" | json | unwrap duration(value_page_load_time) [$__auto]) by (meta_page_url)
quantile_over_time(0.50, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=measurement" | json | unwrap duration(value_dom_interactive_time) [$__auto]) by (meta_page_url)
quantile_over_time(0.95, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=measurement" | json | unwrap duration(value_dom_interactive_time) [$__auto]) by (meta_page_url)

quantile_over_time(0.50, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=measurement" | json | trace_context_trace_id!="" | unwrap duration(value_resource_fetch_duration) [$__auto]) by (meta_page_url)

quantile_over_time(0.95, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=measurement" | json | trace_context_trace_id!="" | unwrap duration(value_resource_fetch_duration) [$__auto]) by (meta_page_url)
quantile_over_time(0.50, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=web-vital" | json | name="TTFB" | unwrap value [$__auto]) by (meta_page_url)
quantile_over_time(0.95, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=web-vital" | json | name="TTFB" | unwrap value [$__auto]) by (meta_page_url)
sum(rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=exception" [$__auto]))
sum by(session_id) (rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=event" | json | type="click" [$__auto]))
avg by(session_id) (avg_over_time({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=measurement" | json | unwrap duration(session_attributes_session_duration) [$__auto]))
{service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=log" | json
sum by(level) (rate({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=log" | json [$__auto]))
topk(10, sum by(meta_page_url) (count_over_time({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=measurement" | json | meta_page_url!="" [$__auto])))
count(count by(meta_user_id) (count_over_time({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | json | meta_user_id!="" [$__auto])))
count(count by(session_id) (count_over_time({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} | json | session_id!="" [$__auto])))
avg(avg_over_time({service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=measurement" | json | unwrap duration(session_attributes_session_duration) [$__auto]))
quantile_over_time(0.95, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=measurement" | json | unwrap duration(value_page_load_time) [$__auto])
quantile_over_time(0.50, {service_name=~"$service", deployment_environment="$env"} |= "kind=web-vital" | json | name="LCP" | unwrap value [$__auto]) by (meta_page_url)
